Dialogue: 1,0:19:19.15,0:19:22.18,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,勝手に仲間にすんな
Dialogue: 1,0:19:25.28,0:19:26.25,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,あれ
Dialogue: 1,0:19:26.25,0:19:28.85,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,私　何してたんだっけ
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.53,0:19:31.53,JP-Main-Down,Group,0,0,0,,茸　茸
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.80,0:19:34.29,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,みんな　茸に一種を乗っ取られてるんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:19:34.29,0:19:34.98,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,どうすんの
Dialogue: 1,0:19:34.98,0:19:37.66,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,逃げるにしても　こんなに囲まれてたら
Dialogue: 1,0:19:39.09,0:19:40.44,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ゴーヤ
Dialogue: 1,0:19:40.44,0:19:41.50,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,もしかしたら
Dialogue: 1,0:19:43.49,0:19:44.96,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,あとは任せた
Dialogue: 1,0:19:44.96,0:19:45.59,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,ええ
Dialogue: 1,0:19:45.59,0:19:46.37,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,まで
Dialogue: 1,0:19:46.37,0:19:50.20,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ゴーヤ
Dialogue: 1,0:19:53.35,0:19:55.67,JP-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,やめて やめてください
Dialogue: 1,0:19:55.67,0:19:59.68,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,茸に寄生された奴らでそれでいいのか
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.68,0:20:02.91,JP-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,やめ　ラッチてんだろうがよ
Dialogue: 1,0:20:04.24,0:20:05.17,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,あの
Dialogue: 1,0:20:05.17,0:20:05.85,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,松茸さん
Dialogue: 1,0:20:05.85,0:20:07.56,JP-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,あんだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:20:07.56,0:20:08.90,JP-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,ああもう
Dialogue: 1,0:20:08.90,0:20:10.75,JP-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,しゃしゃってんじゃねえよ
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.75,0:20:12.76,JP-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,せっかく親切でしてやってんのに
Dialogue: 1,0:20:12.76,0:20:14.12,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,親切
Dialogue: 1,0:20:14.12,0:20:17.05,JP-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,うちらは好きで茸やってんの
Dialogue: 1,0:20:17.05,0:20:19.22,JP-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,こんなクソみたいなノーフューチャー世界で
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.22,0:20:20.45,JP-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,何十年も生きるより
Dialogue: 1,0:20:20.45,0:20:23.22,JP-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,茸生やした　ハッピー　ヒッピー　アンドヒッキーで
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.22,0:20:26.16,JP-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,一二年で死ぬ方がだぜっつの
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.16,0:20:28.24,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,一二年で死ぬ
Dialogue: 1,0:20:28.24,0:20:30.43,JP-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,池袋とか行ってどうすんだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:20:30.43,0:20:31.28,JP-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,無駄無駄
Dialogue: 1,0:20:31.56,0:20:34.60,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,私は　会いたい友達がいて
Dialogue: 1,0:20:34.60,0:20:35.80,JP-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,会ってどうする
Dialogue: 1,0:20:35.80,0:20:38.15,JP-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,つうか　どうせ会えねえって
Dialogue: 1,0:20:38.15,0:20:39.86,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,でもやっぱ行く
Dialogue: 1,0:20:39.86,0:20:42.00,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,行って確かめないと納得できない
Dialogue: 1,0:20:42.00,0:20:43.68,JP-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,馬鹿じゃねえの
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.68,0:20:45.97,JP-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,お前らはせいぜい惨めにあがいて
Dialogue: 1,0:20:45.97,0:20:48.30,JP-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,血反吐吐いて死にそうくなってやら
Dialogue: 1,0:20:48.30,0:20:49.63,JP-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,もう知らねえ
Dialogue: 1,0:20:54.13,0:20:55.14,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,行こう
Dialogue: 1,0:20:57.49,0:20:59.60,JP-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,つっ　勝手にしな
Dialogue: 1,0:21:03.38,0:21:04.43,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,あの
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.43,0:21:06.67,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,食料　ありがとう
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.82,0:21:09.50,JP-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,知らねえよ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:24.71,0:21:26.42,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,茸が
Dialogue: 1,0:21:26.78,0:21:28.94,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,どんな感じなんだろうね
Dialogue: 1,0:21:28.94,0:21:31.08,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,玲実ちゃんちょっと生えてたよ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:31.08,0:21:32.39,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,撫子ちゃんだって
Dialogue: 1,0:21:33.77,0:21:35.44,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,もっとがっつり生えたら
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.44,0:21:38.02,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,このまま死んじゃってもいいって思っちゃうのかな
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.02,0:21:40.90,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,たしかにちょっといい気分だったかもね
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.90,0:21:42.29,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,ふわふわって
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.29,0:21:45.37,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,なんか不思議っていうか　変な感じだった
Dialogue: 1,0:21:45.37,0:21:46.70,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,ていうかさ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:46.70,0:21:48.92,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,みんな私に感謝すべき
Dialogue: 1,0:21:48.92,0:21:49.82,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,感謝って
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.82,0:21:51.31,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,助けてあげたでしょ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.31,0:21:52.96,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,はいはい　感謝感謝
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.96,0:21:54.17,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,適当すぎる
Dialogue: 1,0:21:54.17,0:21:55.13,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,うーちょっと
