Comment: 0,0:02:13.50,0:02:15.50,ZH-Main-Down,,0,0,0,,正文
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.50,0:02:18.52,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,大家是東吾野的居民嗎
