Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.14,0:02:22.36,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,是的 這是列車
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.36,0:02:24.31,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,好久沒有見到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.31,0:02:26.70,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,各位是從哪裡來到這裡的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.13,0:02:28.53,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,隔壁吾野來的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.86,0:02:30.06,ZH-Main-Down,Resident,0,0,0,,原來是吾野
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.41,0:02:31.92,ZH-Main-Down,Resident,0,0,0,,吾野啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.37,0:02:33.78,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,那可真是難得
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.78,0:02:35.95,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,吾野現在距離這裡很遠的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.95,0:02:37.71,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,一路上很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.71,0:02:39.46,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊 還行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.46,0:02:41.51,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,吾野的大家還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.23,0:02:44.95,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,好倒是挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.95,0:02:46.39,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,務必培養
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.39,0:02:49.81,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,不對 請讓我們盡地主之儀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.81,0:02:54.07,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,好在在東吾野 人口相對較少
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.07,0:02:55.92,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,家裡有許多空置的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.92,0:02:57.36,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,好耶 幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.36,0:02:57.98,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,務必前來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.98,0:02:58.72,ZH-Main-Down,Resident,0,0,0,,{\an8}是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.22,0:02:59.24,ZH-Main-Down,Resident,0,0,0,,是呀是呀
