Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.45,0:03:04.45,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,這點小錢不用介意啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.45,0:03:05.36,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.36,0:03:07.06,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,非常感謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.99,0:03:12.42,ZH-Main-Down,Resident,0,0,0,,您好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.79,0:03:14.42,ZH-Main-Down,Group,0,0,0,,您好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.70,0:03:16.76,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,感覺這裡的人都很友好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.76,0:03:18.24,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,和吾野相比大相徑庭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.24,0:03:19.99,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,吾野都是肉食貪吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.99,0:03:21.98,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,夏日祭的核心都是吃吃吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.98,0:03:25.51,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,確實 神社的供奉會放什麼東西呢
