Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.73,0:03:32.30,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,用吾野的特產明明挺好 比如大米 苦瓜 中筋小麥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.30,0:03:33.76,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,苦瓜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.76,0:03:34.46,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.46,0:03:37.56,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,松茸小姐 難道您不喜歡苦瓜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.56,0:03:38.94,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,啊 並不是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.94,0:03:41.23,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,我不是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.23,0:03:43.18,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,畢竟它並不可愛嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.18,0:03:45.66,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,再說 苦瓜與櫛瓜 還有辣椒相比
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.66,0:03:47.18,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,真的太土裡土氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.18,0:03:48.65,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,但是我挺喜歡的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.65,0:03:50.82,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,也就只有小晶你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.82,0:03:52.95,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我們應該沒問題的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.95,0:03:55.04,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我們到底能否抵達池袋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.04,0:03:57.82,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,現在我們根本不知道 會發生什麼事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.11,0:04:00.41,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,{\an8}松茸小姐 您有去過池袋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.83,0:04:04.67,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,以前我住在那裡 但後來又回來東吾野這了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.67,0:04:05.61,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,挺好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.61,0:04:06.50,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,那裡怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.50,0:04:08.16,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,比這裡更加城市化對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.16,0:04:09.28,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,我想是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.28,0:04:10.61,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,我認為是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.61,0:04:11.96,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,認為的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.96,0:04:13.21,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,實在對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.21,0:04:15.30,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,現在的我已經對它不感興趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.56,0:04:18.03,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,這個女孩 你有見到過她 或者類似她的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.03,0:04:19.65,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,在池袋那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.65,0:04:20.47,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.47,0:04:22.69,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,唉 果然是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.56,0:04:28.36,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,好 剪好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.36,0:04:30.05,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,前瀏海這樣可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.05,0:04:30.99,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,挺好挺好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.99,0:04:33.11,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,真的是 好好看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.11,0:04:34.97,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香剪的頭髮沒有不好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.78,0:04:36.67,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,來拍張照片吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.93,0:04:38.38,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,紀念一下它
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.81,0:04:45.19,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,靜留
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.19,0:04:46.44,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.44,0:04:47.80,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.80,0:04:50.96,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,欸 挺正式的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.96,0:04:51.77,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,玲實
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.77,0:04:53.08,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.08,0:04:57.48,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,東吾野這裡賓至如歸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.48,0:05:00.04,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,特別是水霧三溫暖很推薦噢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.04,0:05:01.41,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,說起推薦的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.41,0:05:02.97,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,絕對要試一試
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.97,0:05:04.73,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,請務必蒸一蒸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.73,0:05:05.81,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,啊 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.12,0:05:07.72,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,那麼請您稍等片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.15,0:05:12.48,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我們是不是有汗臭味了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.48,0:05:14.28,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但說起來 三溫暖在哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.88,0:05:15.87,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.87,0:05:17.83,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,欸 挺精緻的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.52,0:05:23.79,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,哇 好厲害的水霧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.79,0:05:25.53,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,挺好的 快進去快進去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.53,0:05:27.45,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,感覺就像排毒一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.01,0:05:29.21,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,我就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.21,0:05:30.23,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.23,0:05:33.30,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,現在正好洗洗衣服順便晾乾呀 小晶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.30,0:05:34.34,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,不 我不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.34,0:05:37.10,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,先不說一個人 全部人一起洗我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.10,0:05:38.20,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我明白啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.20,0:05:40.29,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,裸體被別人看到會很害羞的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.29,0:05:41.97,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,明明不用這麼在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.97,0:05:43.33,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,總而言之你們洗就好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.73,0:05:47.52,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,總感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.52,0:05:50.44,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,從吾野出來到底是不是好事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.44,0:05:53.44,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,但是一個人在吾野待著也不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.44,0:06:12.11,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,打擾一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.40,0:06:15.55,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,蒸完三溫暖後 我想你們肚子應該會很餓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.55,0:06:18.01,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,啊 感謝您的款待
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.57,0:06:22.80,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,蘑菇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.80,0:06:24.23,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,您不喜歡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.23,0:06:25.12,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.12,0:06:26.85,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,啊並不 還行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.85,0:06:28.30,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.30,0:06:30.43,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,就著煮熟的米飯會很好吃的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.43,0:06:32.25,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,畢竟這是松茸呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.49,0:06:34.94,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,您有享受過水霧三溫暖了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.94,0:06:37.23,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,啊有 大概蒸了蒸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.23,0:06:38.15,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,和其他人一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.15,0:06:40.23,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,這真的太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.23,0:06:42.84,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,今天請好好休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.84,0:06:45.04,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,輕輕鬆鬆的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.04,0:06:45.86,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.37,0:06:56.85,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,小晶這些是什麼 盛宴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.85,0:06:58.16,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,發生什麼事了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.16,0:07:00.84,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,剛才松茸小姐拿過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.14,0:07:02.83,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,真的無微不至呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.83,0:07:05.38,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,剛剛蒸完三溫暖 肚子一下子就餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.38,0:07:06.59,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我們一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.59,0:07:08.08,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我要吃「豬肉卷明天見」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.08,0:07:09.12,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.48,0:07:10.31,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.31,0:07:11.41,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,這不奇怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.41,0:07:12.01,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,奇怪什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.01,0:07:12.98,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,這裡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.98,0:07:14.10,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,欸 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.10,0:07:15.11,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,不挺親切的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.11,0:07:16.45,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,除了頭上長著蘑菇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.45,0:07:17.21,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.21,0:07:18.50,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,為什麼長著蘑菇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.50,0:07:19.30,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,問問他們唄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.30,0:07:21.13,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,這樣不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.13,0:07:21.96,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,欸 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.96,0:07:22.89,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.89,0:07:25.92,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,好比如 說別人禿頭的自己也是禿頭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.92,0:07:27.32,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,禮貌 禮儀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.32,0:07:28.23,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.23,0:07:29.10,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.10,0:07:31.17,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,長著蘑菇也沒什麼問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.17,0:07:33.69,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,吾野的可都是動物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.69,0:07:35.86,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,這裡的人到不會整天嚷嚷吃肉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.86,0:07:36.90,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,而且還挺友善的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.90,0:07:38.83,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,東吾野確實是個好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.83,0:07:40.43,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,太悠閒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.11,0:07:57.30,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,玲實
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.30,0:07:58.85,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,吶 玲實醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.85,0:08:01.64,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,你個零分玲實
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.60,0:08:05.88,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,我也能一個人去廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.77,0:08:14.26,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,為什麼三溫暖會給一個單獨的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.26,0:08:16.24,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,而廁所離得那麼遠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.24,0:08:17.94,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,設計好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.11,0:08:24.63,ZH-Main-Down,Resident,0,0,0,,翹首以盼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.63,0:08:26.11,ZH-Main-Down,Resident,0,0,0,,都睡那了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.64,0:08:37.60,ZH-Main-Down,Resident,0,0,0,,果然外來的人真是笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.60,0:08:38.98,ZH-Main-Down,Resident,0,0,0,,毫無懷疑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.98,0:08:40.43,ZH-Main-Down,Resident,0,0,0,,正如所你所說一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.43,0:08:41.67,ZH-Main-Down,Resident,0,0,0,,快點開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.67,0:08:43.44,ZH-Main-Down,Resident,0,0,0,,越早來越好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.44,0:08:45.46,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,讓她們成為我們的「伙伴」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.46,0:08:48.49,ZH-Main-Down,Resident,0,0,0,,這對她們來說是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.49,0:08:50.38,ZH-Main-Down,Resident,0,0,0,,我們這群「人」要拯救她們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.00,0:08:54.55,ZH-Main-Down,Resident,0,0,0,,是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.50,0:09:13.65,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.02,0:09:18.44,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,靜留
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.26,0:09:21.11,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我都驚醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.11,0:09:21.96,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,怎麼了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.27,0:09:31.45,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,松茸小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.78,0:09:35.42,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,畢竟是在陌生的地方 定是做了個噩夢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.42,0:09:37.33,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,得了吧讓我好好休息會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.33,0:09:39.30,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,小晶 快點給松茸小姐道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.57,0:09:42.26,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,大聲吵鬧 快點說聲對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.26,0:09:43.85,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.85,0:09:45.69,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,請好好休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.01,0:09:49.09,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,再回籠睡覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.09,0:09:50.81,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,這裡 真的很可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.81,0:09:52.18,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,早點離開這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.18,0:09:53.54,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.54,0:09:55.06,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,小晶真的是個膽小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.06,0:09:56.30,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.30,0:09:57.72,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,我才不是害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.72,0:09:59.77,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你和她一起睡覺吧 玲實
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.77,0:10:00.52,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,哈 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.52,0:10:02.15,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,小晶睡相很不好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.15,0:10:04.06,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,小晶我陪你去廁所吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.06,0:10:05.68,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,你還沒有去對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.68,0:10:06.79,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.31,0:10:08.62,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.62,0:10:09.92,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我在的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.92,0:10:12.12,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,不要亂走動 撫子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.12,0:10:13.50,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.16,0:10:18.02,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,看不見星星啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.38,0:10:20.45,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,明天也是陰天嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.18,0:10:25.83,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,你們都被騙了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.83,0:10:27.23,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,是陰謀論啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.23,0:10:29.61,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,小晶很喜歡「控濟會」嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.61,0:10:30.81,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,是「共濟會」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.81,0:10:32.06,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.06,0:10:33.43,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我們馬上就離開了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.36,0:10:37.54,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊敲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.54,0:10:38.83,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,就一個晚上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.83,0:10:40.37,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,是不是光照太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.37,0:10:41.53,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,不會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.53,0:10:42.71,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,一直都是陰雲天氣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.71,0:10:45.65,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,還有 這裡和吾野相比更加潮濕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.65,0:10:47.87,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,結果 它們看起來長得挺健壯的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.87,0:10:49.24,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊 果實已經成熟了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.18,0:10:55.61,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,這個苦味可是很有營養的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.17,0:10:58.54,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,感覺你們的反應挺大的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.54,0:10:59.91,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,欸 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.91,0:11:01.97,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,畢竟 在陽光的直射下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.97,0:11:04.64,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,全部的生物都會產生不良的影響
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.64,0:11:05.88,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,又熱 又乾燥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.88,0:11:08.64,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,被光照燒死是宇宙不變的定律
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.64,0:11:09.89,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.89,0:11:12.11,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,然而這個 還能健康茁壯成長
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.11,0:11:14.24,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,就是這樣瞧不起我們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.24,0:11:17.11,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,就像這樣 就因為存在玉米還有陽光之類的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.11,0:11:19.07,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,世界已經變得非常奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.07,0:11:20.37,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.37,0:11:24.38,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,總而言之這些苦 全部都給我扯下來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.38,0:11:25.76,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊 行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.76,0:11:26.98,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我就打算這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.98,0:11:28.05,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,令人恐懼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.04,0:11:31.86,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,原來她這麼討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.86,0:11:34.85,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,總而言之 先把這些全部都摘下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.85,0:11:36.37,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,感覺像是一個陰謀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.37,0:11:38.46,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,陰謀 是什麼 誰的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.46,0:11:40.97,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,是為了阻礙我們不讓離開
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.97,0:11:42.59,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,你又開始胡說八道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.59,0:11:43.50,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,這才不是胡話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.75,0:11:44.55,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,小晶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.55,0:11:46.64,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,和我一起對抗苦瓜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.64,0:11:49.47,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,這期間 玲實和撫子去買點東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.47,0:11:50.16,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.16,0:11:52.78,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,有能夠長期保存的食物會更好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.78,0:11:53.95,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.95,0:11:54.93,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.93,0:11:56.59,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,很多事情要留個心眼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.59,0:11:57.66,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,撫子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.66,0:11:59.65,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,東吾野有便利商店嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.65,0:12:00.46,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,挺有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.46,0:12:01.14,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,玲實
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.14,0:12:02.47,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.03,0:12:07.41,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,靜 玲 撫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.33,0:12:13.69,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,你們在想什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.69,0:12:15.41,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,不行 不能這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.41,0:12:16.64,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,又為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.64,0:12:18.50,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那邊就拜託你了 小晶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.50,0:12:20.72,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,我們不是說要去池袋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.72,0:12:21.72,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,會去的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.72,0:12:23.34,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,那你是為什麼缺乏信心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.34,0:12:26.35,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,為什麼你會如此樂不思蜀 我根本不明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.84,0:12:29.82,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,我去找她們倆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.75,0:12:42.06,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,這是什麼鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.06,0:12:43.09,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,慘了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.83,0:12:56.14,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,玲實 撫子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.14,0:12:58.06,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,他們說免費給我們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.06,0:12:59.85,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,真的可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.85,0:13:02.16,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,我們已經不再需要它們了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.16,0:13:02.84,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,已經
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.12,0:13:07.59,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,你 你們比起我們更加需要這些東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.59,0:13:09.73,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,哇 超級親切的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.73,0:13:12.33,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,有了這些的話 生存暫時是沒什麼問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.33,0:13:15.20,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,就算對我們這麼好 也不能回報些什麼給你們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.20,0:13:16.96,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,我們馬上就要離開了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.96,0:13:20.30,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,和吾野的不同 東吾野的大家更為親切
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.30,0:13:21.44,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,而且還很冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.44,0:13:23.10,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,博愛精神都滿溢了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.10,0:13:25.29,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,這些東西沒什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.29,0:13:27.24,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,曾經的東吾野
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.24,0:13:31.44,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,很多人也是沮喪擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.44,0:13:34.36,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,但是 7G事件後我們察覺到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.82,0:13:38.03,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,比起面朝黃土背朝天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.03,0:13:42.32,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,更好的生活 便是在短暫的人生中充實享受時間
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.45,0:13:47.62,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,如此決定後 再也不會忍氣吞聲了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.97,0:13:50.68,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,挺深奧的呀 松茸小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.68,0:13:53.88,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,這種心境 我們是否也能領悟到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.88,0:13:55.92,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,會的 肯定能理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.92,0:13:58.36,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,你們大家 很快就會的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.70,0:14:00.34,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,吶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.34,0:14:01.82,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,快點走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.82,0:14:03.74,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,靜留她肯定會擔心我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.74,0:14:05.78,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,擔心 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.78,0:14:08.56,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,好想成為像松茸小姐一樣的存在呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.56,0:14:10.89,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,不行 我們必須要去池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.89,0:14:12.64,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,欸 池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.64,0:14:14.26,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,東吾野這不好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.26,0:14:15.24,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,也不錯呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.24,0:14:16.40,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.40,0:14:18.89,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,我們必須要去見葉香的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.21,0:14:23.49,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,靜留
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.49,0:14:24.67,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,苦瓜根本沒有修剪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.67,0:14:26.10,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,苦瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.10,0:14:27.50,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊 苦瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.85,0:14:31.13,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,這樣做有什麼意義所在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.13,0:14:31.86,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.86,0:14:34.80,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我們真的能去到池袋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.80,0:14:36.87,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,感覺我們根本到不了那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.87,0:14:38.03,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.03,0:14:39.87,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,不是昨天才出來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.87,0:14:43.41,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,就算到了那裡 感覺也不會改變什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.41,0:14:45.89,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,你不是說必須要見到葉香嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.89,0:14:49.80,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,嗯 就算一直等她也無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.80,0:14:52.96,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,再者說她也不一定記得我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.96,0:14:55.21,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,見都沒見到根本不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.21,0:14:55.99,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,你們倆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.99,0:14:57.99,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,玲實和撫子你們也說點什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.99,0:14:59.01,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,想睡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.87,0:15:04.08,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,小晶你太吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.08,0:15:07.12,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,不是餓殍滿地 孤苦伶仃地活著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.12,0:15:10.45,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,曇花一現 樂天知命才是真理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.17,0:15:14.49,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,已經不行了 完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.98,0:15:15.89,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,五點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.20,0:15:21.99,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,這裡是小晶 現在在東吾野
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.26,0:15:25.93,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,這裡是吾野 報告狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.36,0:15:27.71,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,蘑菇很多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.71,0:15:28.87,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,遍地都是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.87,0:15:30.45,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,請教蘑菇的危險程度
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.90,0:15:32.71,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,什麼 蘑菇嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.71,0:15:33.40,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.40,0:15:36.25,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,香濃松茸 鮮美占地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.25,0:15:38.55,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,松露菌不是豬而是狗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.55,0:15:39.87,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,白色比黑色
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.22,0:15:44.51,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,總而言之 蘑菇就是圓圓的 通常為環形東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.51,0:15:47.63,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,據說這是一個關於妖精和魔女的死亡傳言
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.63,0:15:51.30,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,實際上菌類的生長與死亡相伴 很容易就能觀察到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.30,0:15:54.98,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,據說雷擊之後很容易出現這種情況 就是所謂的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.98,0:15:56.89,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,誰他媽管你打不打雷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.89,0:15:59.38,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,快點告訴我避免或是逃離蘑菇侵害的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.38,0:16:01.88,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,把蘑菇給吃光 吧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.88,0:16:03.89,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,吧吧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.44,0:16:10.29,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,不要將重要的情報消耗在吃蘑菇身上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.80,0:16:21.77,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,苦瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.51,0:16:24.88,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,不要過來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.86,0:16:29.58,ZH-Main-Down,Resident,0,0,0,,為什麼要反抗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.58,0:16:31.60,ZH-Main-Down,Resident,0,0,0,,直接過來這不好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.60,0:16:32.59,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,別廢話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.59,0:16:35.14,ZH-Main-Down,Resident,0,0,0,,如今你苟且偷生 又有什麼好處
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.14,0:16:37.81,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,變成蘑菇才是一種損失
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.81,0:16:38.83,ZH-Main-Down,King Oyster,0,0,0,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.83,0:16:40.26,ZH-Main-Down,King Oyster,0,0,0,,蘑菇可沒有煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.26,0:16:41.80,ZH-Main-Down,Enoki,0,0,0,,蘑菇也沒有痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.80,0:16:43.64,ZH-Main-Down,Fly Agaric,0,0,0,,蘑菇還不用思考
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.99,0:16:46.36,ZH-Main-Down,Group,0,0,0,,大家都變成蘑菇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.36,0:16:47.44,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,絕對不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.74,0:16:49.15,ZH-Main-Down,Resident,0,0,0,,很開心的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.78,0:16:54.65,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,蘑菇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.65,0:16:55.81,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,蘑菇軍團
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.57,0:17:02.92,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,小晶你太吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.92,0:17:04.70,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,好想輕輕鬆鬆地離開呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.70,0:17:08.08,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,什麼也不用想 輕飄飄的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.08,0:17:09.66,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,別光蹲在那啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.66,0:17:12.14,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,你們說去池袋到底是為了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.14,0:17:13.10,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.10,0:17:16.13,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,難道你不是去池袋趕潮流的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.13,0:17:17.26,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,時尚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.26,0:17:19.38,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,難道不是為了去見葉香嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.65,0:17:21.85,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.85,0:17:25.79,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,根本不是在這 給它們培養蘑菇的時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.75,0:17:27.78,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.40,0:17:33.86,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香什麼的 自顧自就離開吾野了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.86,0:17:35.69,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,自顧自地消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.69,0:17:37.21,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,她怎樣都無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.21,0:17:38.38,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.38,0:17:39.82,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,她是「朋友」才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.82,0:17:41.55,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.55,0:17:43.53,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,到底是不是朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.83,0:17:46.81,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,分別的時候我們也還不是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.81,0:17:49.46,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,再說了葉香所想的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.75,0:17:52.63,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我根本一點也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.91,0:17:57.05,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,靜留 學習有助於培養情操
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.05,0:17:59.64,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,欸 損人也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.99,0:18:04.40,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,未來發展意向的調查問卷還沒出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.40,0:18:05.96,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,前途啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.96,0:18:07.53,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,有沒想要成為的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.53,0:18:08.47,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,有的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.47,0:18:10.01,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,想要成為非常明智的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.01,0:18:12.02,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,那可要好好學習
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.02,0:18:13.37,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,還要學習啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.73,0:18:17.05,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.05,0:18:17.73,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,有的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.73,0:18:19.17,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,什麼 快說快說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.17,0:18:20.50,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,我想去池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.50,0:18:23.91,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你別騙我 去那坐列車就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.91,0:18:27.59,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我要不要成為吾野柔術綜合格鬥家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.59,0:18:29.69,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,而且 還想和食蟻獸打一架
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.69,0:18:30.82,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,不挺好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.82,0:18:32.31,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,好好回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.31,0:18:33.93,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,好好回答啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.68,0:18:35.83,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.83,0:18:37.00,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.00,0:18:39.54,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,葉香會在池袋等著你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.54,0:18:43.32,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,池袋 葉香 等著我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.06,0:18:50.95,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.25,0:18:51.10,ZH-Main-Down,Shiitake,0,0,0,,{\an8}快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.10,0:18:52.40,ZH-Main-Down,Enoki,0,0,0,,別這樣 快放手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.30,0:18:59.70,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,到底是否會變得糟糕 取決於我們 自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.70,0:19:02.39,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,靜留
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.28,0:19:06.79,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你誰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.25,0:19:09.56,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,開個玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.56,0:19:11.02,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,稍微來點輕鬆與關愛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.84,0:19:13.17,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.17,0:19:15.36,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,一起拔掉撫子和玲實的蘑菇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.36,0:19:15.92,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.92,0:19:18.38,ZH-Main-Down,King Oyster,0,0,0,,難道你們不懂得幸福嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.12,0:19:19.15,ZH-Main-Down,Porcini,0,0,0,,{\an8}我們要守護我們的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.15,0:19:22.18,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,別擅自把我們變成你的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.28,0:19:26.25,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.25,0:19:28.85,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我們 到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.53,0:19:31.53,ZH-Main-Down,Group,0,0,0,,蘑菇 蘑菇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.80,0:19:34.29,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,各位 你們被蘑菇占據了思想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.29,0:19:34.98,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,要怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.98,0:19:37.66,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,就算要逃跑 但被這麼多人圍著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.09,0:19:40.44,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,苦瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.44,0:19:41.50,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,難不成
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.49,0:19:44.96,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,剩下的交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.96,0:19:45.59,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,欸欸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.59,0:19:46.37,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,等會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.37,0:19:50.20,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,苦瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.35,0:19:55.67,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,不要 請快點住手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.67,0:19:59.68,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,被蘑菇寄生 成為它們的一員真的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.68,0:20:02.91,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,不要 別揪著老娘不放
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.24,0:20:05.17,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.17,0:20:05.85,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,松茸小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.85,0:20:07.56,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,你這人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.56,0:20:08.90,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,啊真的是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.90,0:20:10.75,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,別擱著礙手礙腳的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.75,0:20:12.76,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,明明那麼親切幫助你們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.76,0:20:14.12,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,親切
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.12,0:20:17.05,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,我們大家是喜歡蘑菇才成為的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.05,0:20:19.22,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,這個沒有未來的狗屎世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.22,0:20:20.45,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,比起活幾十年
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.45,0:20:23.22,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,不如像蘑菇一樣 開心 嬉皮 並蝸居
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.22,0:20:26.16,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,並在一兩年後就死去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.16,0:20:28.24,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,一兩年後就死去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.24,0:20:30.43,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,想去池袋什麼的 要怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.43,0:20:31.28,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.56,0:20:34.60,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我只是有個朋友 想見她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.60,0:20:35.80,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,見了又如何
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.80,0:20:38.15,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,不如說 你永遠也見不到她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.15,0:20:39.86,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但是我還要去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.86,0:20:42.00,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,必須要去看看 才能接受與否
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.00,0:20:43.68,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,你是笨蛋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.68,0:20:45.97,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,你們這群人只不過是在苦苦掙扎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.97,0:20:48.30,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,最終會口吐鮮血 然後死去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.30,0:20:49.63,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,Who care?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.13,0:20:55.14,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.49,0:20:59.60,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,切 自以為是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.38,0:21:04.43,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.43,0:21:06.67,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,感謝您能給予我們食物與水
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.82,0:21:09.50,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,主不在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.71,0:21:26.42,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,蘑菇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.78,0:21:28.94,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,會是什麼樣的感覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.94,0:21:31.08,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,玲實你稍微長大了一點呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.08,0:21:32.39,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,撫子也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.77,0:21:35.44,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,如果它生長得更茁壯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.44,0:21:38.02,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我不知道會不會就這麼被死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.02,0:21:40.90,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,但感覺確實挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.90,0:21:42.29,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,輕飄飄的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.29,0:21:45.37,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,感覺有些不可思議 或是感覺怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.37,0:21:46.70,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,要我說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.70,0:21:48.92,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,大家都應該感謝我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.92,0:21:49.82,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.82,0:21:51.31,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,畢竟我拯救了你們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.31,0:21:52.96,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊對對 感謝你感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.96,0:21:54.17,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,太隨便了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.17,0:21:55.13,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,欸等會
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.13,0:21:56.38,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,波奇你太無禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.66,0:21:58.73,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,怎麼了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.73,0:21:59.97,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,沒什麼
